A CUE unites a MEDIA ASSET, a MEDIA HANDLER (i.e. player), a FIRING CONDITION, and a TARGET GROUP.

A SESSION handles ongoing functionality that needs to be run through the app delegate: audio, networking.

An EPISODE prepares and plays a set of CUES for a set of TARGET GROUPS.

